        "timestamp": "2019-04-09 08:44:24.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nBogumil, Is it possible to avoid keeping many CSAR for UT. Instead, can you test the functionality by using sample file, ex sample manifest file, in which have expected entries. \n\nAlso, we need to maintain the separate list of test cases for PNF and VNF. otherwise, always it will endup in failure.",
