        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-04-09 08:51:58.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\n1. I used CSAR files, because it is really hard to test code using current implementation/framework used in vnfsdk.\nI will try to make changes in vnfsdk to make it more testable.\n2. I have correction with separate list of test cases, but first this change must be merged.",
